<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="worse-adv">worse <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /wɜːs/    美 /wɜːrs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>更坏；更糟；(病) 更重；更猛烈：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I slept worse in hot weather. 
热天我更加睡不好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It is raining worse than ever. 
雨下得比以往都大。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="worse-and-worse">worse and worse</h3>
<p>1.<strong>越来越坏；每况愈下：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The weather is getting worse and worse. 
天气变得越来越坏。</p></div>

<h3 id="worse-off">worse off</h3>
<p>1.<strong>更穷的；更糟的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Unfortunately his father died,leaving the family even worse off.
很不幸，他的父亲过世了，使得家里更加贫困。</p><footer>人教④-3</footer></div></div>